Get free icons in Glyph Neue design style

Glyph Neue is a decorative icon style. It is an outline version of the Pastel style.

  • This cartoonish icon pack is based on a 128x128 px canvas.
  • All the icons have a bold border.

As well as Cute Outline, Dotted, Hand Drawn, and Gradient Line icon packs, these elegant free images fit desktop or web applications, newsletters, landing pages, and mobile app screens.

Also, the images work well as monochrome clipart for presentations, infographics, card design, and educational projects.

Download Glyph Neue icons in different themes for UI and graphic design.

The free graphics are pixel-perfect to fit your design and are available in both PNG and vector.
